25:05.233 --> 25:10.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A hard Brexit would mean the
reimposition of import tariffs
and restrict the migration

25:11.133 --> 25:13.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of E.U. citizens.

25:13.333 --> 25:16.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Marianna Kolookotroni from
southern Greece has been running
this stall for seven years.

25:16.966 --> 25:20.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARIANNA KOLOOKOTRONI,
Vendor: It is a little
bit scary, I have to say.

25:20.766 --> 25:25.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I am trying to remain
positive, and I really hope
that nothing is going to change,

25:27.166 --> 25:30.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
because it's not in the
interests of anyone, really.

25:30.333 --> 25:35.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Thea Wunder
is from Italy's border with
Austria, and she fears customs

25:37.800 --> 25:41.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
