in value after the referendum.

25:45.266 --> 25:50.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
THEA WUNDER, Vendor: So the
exchange rate, it has already
affected it, so the euro has

25:51.400 --> 25:52.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
much more value
than it used to be.

25:52.900 --> 25:56.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, I already -- the business
already loses money on that.

25:56.066 --> 26:01.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there's only so much we
can put our prices up to be
still fair and competitive.

26:03.600 --> 26:06.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Britain's
tourism and hospitality
industry generates 10
percent of the nation's

26:08.366 --> 26:10.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
