workers; 25 percent of the three
million people in this field

26:15.233 --> 26:16.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
comes from the European Union.

26:16.766 --> 26:19.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The duty manager Bashir Issa
is originally from Somalia.

26:19.733 --> 26:22.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BASHIR ISSA, Duty Manager:
British people are not working
in the industry, and we need

26:22.933 --> 26:27.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to have the European community
or anywhere else in the
world coming to us with their

26:29.333 --> 26:31.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
expertise, helping us
and the industry to grow.

26:31.933 --> 26:35.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: The
industry wants to preserve
freedom of movement, and
is lobbying the government

26:35.266 --> 26:36.266 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
hard.

26:36.266 --> 26:38.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Spokesman Vernon Hunte:

26:38.766 --> 26:40.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
VERNON HUNTE, Hospitality
Industry Spokesman: We
believe that the economy
must be put first,

26:40.866 --> 26:43.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that the British industry,
especially, of course, from
our perspective, hospitality

26:43.933 --> 26:46.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
businesses, their needs and
requirements are put first.

26:46.333 --> 26:48.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NICK WARD, Britain: Independent
doesn't mean isolated.

26:48.800 --> 26:50.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's an interactive
independence.

26:50.866 --> 26:55.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Where do people get this idea
that, when you're independent,
you're closing your doors?

26:55.500 --> 26:57.100 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
They're mad.

26:57.100 --> 27:00.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Nick
Ward relishes the
freedom of motorcycling.

27:00.666 --> 27:04.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Independence and national
sovereignty drive his
continued support for Brexit.

27:04.466 --> 27:08.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
NICK WARD: There's more
to it than economics.

27:08.000 --> 27:13.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What Brexit actually means is
that you want to control your
own borders and you want to

27:13.733 --> 27:15.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
make your own laws.

27:15.233 --> 27:18.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that is your starting
point for negotiations.

27:18.700 --> 27:21.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why do so many people want to
come here in the first place?

27:21.366 --> 27:26.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Britain is probably the
least racist or xenophobic
country in all of Europe.

27:26.333 --> 27:28.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Try being black and
playing football in Poland.

27:28.900 --> 27:33.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We want to interact and
we want to maintain this
beautiful island for
everybody and generations

27:35.833 --> 27:37.866 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
to come.

27:37.866 --> 27:41.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MALCOLM BRABANT: British
attitudes towards
Europe are turning, as
people belatedly agree

27:41.333 --> 27:46.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with the so-called remainers
that pre-referendum,
pro-Brexit rhetoric was flawed.

27:48.866 --> 27:52.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Business leaders hope
the prospect of economic
trouble will convince the
government to compromise

27:52.066 --> 27:53.566 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with Brussels.

27:53.566 --> 27:57.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
On Brexit beach, Britain's
schisms are as deep as ever.

27:57.000 --> 28:02.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
