renowned blues musicians

28:19.966 --> 28:24.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
team up on a new album; and
what it's like to be the
first Muslim cover girl.

28:26.933 --> 28:31.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, first, let's turn to
the Senate Republican bill to
overhaul parts of Obamacare.

28:33.333 --> 28:37.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Senate may be in recess
this week, but Majority Leader
Mitch McConnell is working

28:37.033 --> 28:42.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
behind the scenes to craft a
bill that will appeal to enough
Republican votes to pass.

28:43.966 --> 28:48.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
One of the key stumbling blocks,
the provision to cut Medicaid
spending by more than $770

28:49.400 --> 28:51.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
billion over 10 years.

28:51.866 --> 28:56.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That has sparked serious
concern among many governors,
among other reasons, over what

28:58.433 --> 29:01.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
